<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Vieu × Pellera — A Fresh Proposal</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --pearl: #EEEEEE;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --ink: #333333;
    --ink-light: #666666;
    --accent: #7744FF;
    --accent-tint: rgba(119,68,255,0.07);
    --accent-tint-strong: rgba(119,68,255,0.13);
    --red: #FF5363;
    --green: #00EC8A;
    --card-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.07), 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    --radius: 15px;
    --font: 'Share Tech', 'Courier New', monospace;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: var(--font);
    background-color: var(--pearl);
    color: var(--ink);
    min-height: 100vh;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 90% 10%, rgba(119,68,255,0.10) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(circle 1px at 1px 1px, rgba(51,51,51,0.08) 1px, transparent 0);
    background-size: 100% 100%, 28px 28px;
  }

  .page {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 40px 80px;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  .header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .logo-wordmark {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .logo-wordmark span {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .header-meta {
    text-align: right;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ── EYEBROW ── */
  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .hero-body {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), transparent);
    margin: 48px 0;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  /* ── SECTION ── */
  .section {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* ── REFRAME CARD ── */
  .reframe-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 32px;
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .reframe-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius) var(--radius) 0 0;
  }

  .reframe-card p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .reframe-card p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .reframe-card strong {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ── SIGNAL CARDS ── */
  .signals-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .signal-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 24px 20px;
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  }

  .signal-icon {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.10em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: block;
  }

  .signal-card h3 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .signal-card p {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink-light);
  }

  /* ── OFFER CARD ── */
  .offer-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 36px;
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  }

  .offer-card .offer-headline {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .offer-card p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .offer-card p:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .deliverables {
    margin: 24px 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .deliverable-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .deliverable-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  /* ── METRIC CALLOUT ── */
  .metric-strip {
    background: var(--accent-tint);
    border: 1px solid rgba(119,68,255,0.18);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }

  .metric-number {
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .metric-label strong { font-weight: 700; }

  /* ── ASK CARD ── */
  .ask-card {
    background: var(--ink);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 36px;
    color: var(--white);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ask-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -60px; right: -60px;
    width: 200px; height: 200px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(119,68,255,0.35) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ask-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .ask-card h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ask-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  .footer {
    margin-top: 64px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(51,51,51,0.12);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .footer-left { text-transform: uppercase; }

  .footer-mark {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page { padding: 40px 24px 60px; }
    .signals-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .header { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    .header-meta { text-align: left; }
    .metric-strip { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; }
    .metric-number { font-size: 32px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo-wordmark">v<span>ie</span>u</div>
    <div class="header-meta">
      Prepared for Darrin D. Nelson<br>
      EVP Strategic Growth &amp; GTM Enablement<br>
      Pellera Technologies &nbsp;·&nbsp; May 2026
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">A Fresh Start</div>
    <h1>A Different Proposal.<br><em>A Different Motion.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-body">
      The pilot tested one thing: finding warm introductions through Pellera's network.
      That motion requires your team to activate it. In a merger year, that was the wrong ask.
      What follows is a fundamentally different offer - one where Vieu does the work,
      and your AEs receive finished intelligence they can use today.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- WHAT WE HEARD -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">What We Heard</div>
    <div class="reframe-card">
      <p>
        Your team's challenge isn't finding contact data. It's knowing <strong>which accounts to prioritize right now</strong>,
        and walking into a CFO conversation with the context to earn the next one.
      </p>
      <p>
        Cold outreach to senior finance executives at large enterprises has a near-zero conversion rate.
        The window to break through opens when something changes at the account - a new CFO in seat,
        an FP&A team scaling, a competitor platform showing stress. Most AEs find out two quarters late.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>That's the problem Vieu solves.</strong> Not connections. Intelligence - delivered before your AE even knows to look.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- BUYING SIGNALS -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">The Signals That Open Doors</div>
    <div class="signals-grid">
      <div class="signal-card">
        <span class="signal-icon">Signal 01</span>
        <h3>New CFO In Seat</h3>
        <p>A CFO in their first 90 days is actively evaluating tools. The window is now - not six months from now when the stack is locked.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="signal-card">
        <span class="signal-icon">Signal 02</span>
        <h3>FP&A Headcount Growth</h3>
        <p>Active FP&A hiring signals a team scaling beyond its current toolset. IBM Planning Analytics is exactly the conversation to have.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="signal-card">
        <span class="signal-icon">Signal 03</span>
        <h3>Competitor Renewal Window</h3>
        <p>A competing FP&A platform approaching renewal is a live displacement opportunity. Vieu surfaces these before the contract re-signs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- THE OFFER -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">The Offer</div>
    <div class="offer-card">
      <div class="offer-headline">10 Prioritized AWS Pipeline Targets. Delivered. Ready to Deploy.</div>
      <p>
        Using Pellera's ICP - already scoped from our prior engagement - Vieu identifies your top 10
        pipeline opportunities for IBM Planning Analytics this quarter. Each account is selected
        because something is happening there <em>right now</em> that makes it the right moment to call.
      </p>
      <p>For each of the 10 accounts, your AEs receive:</p>
      <div class="deliverables">
        <div class="deliverable-row">
          <div class="deliverable-dot"></div>
          <span>What's happening at the company - the specific signal that makes now the right moment</span>
        </div>
        <div class="deliverable-row">
          <div class="deliverable-dot"></div>
          <span>The right person to contact - CFO or FP&A leader, with context on their mandate</span>
        </div>
        <div class="deliverable-row">
          <div class="deliverable-dot"></div>
          <span>A suggested angle - why this account, why this week, how to frame the conversation</span>
        </div>
        <div class="deliverable-row">
          <div class="deliverable-dot"></div>
          <span>A draft first outreach - ready to send, no research required</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>
        <strong>Your AEs' only job is to decide whether to send it.</strong>
        No setup. No activation work. No asking the team to change how they work.
      </p>

      <div class="metric-strip">
        <div class="metric-number">1</div>
        <div class="metric-label">
          <strong>One meeting. That's the bar.</strong><br>
          One net-new meeting booked with a CFO or FP&A leader at a Vieu-sourced account.
          That's the proof point. Small, concrete, provable - and a foundation to expand from.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- THE ASK -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="ask-card">
      <div class="ask-eyebrow">One Question Before We Build</div>
      <h3>Which 2-3 accounts has your team been trying to crack for months?</h3>
      <p>
        The ones where your AEs have tried every avenue and can't get traction.
        Tell us those accounts - and that's exactly where we start.
        Vieu builds the intelligence package around your most frustrating targets first,
        so the first result you see is on a problem you already know is real.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <div class="footer">
    <div class="footer-left">©Vieu 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Connect to Close &nbsp;|&nbsp; Built on 9B Executive Relationships</div>
    <div class="footer-mark">vieu</div>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
